de.fuberlin.panda.metadata.parsedMetadata

Class ParsedMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fuberlin.panda.metadata.parsedMetadata.ParsedMetadata
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    VirtuosoMetadata, XMLMetadata

    public abstract class ParsedMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class is the internal representation of the metadata parsed from a valid source. It holds the static fields of operations, the different scope types as well as the type information.
    Since:
    05.09.2013
    Author:
    Sebastian Schulz
